import bisect
import math

def count_beautiful_subarrays(A, N, K):
    fp = 1
    for i in range(N):
        left = []
        arr = [0] * 2050
        for j in range(i, N):
            right = A[j]
            bisect.insort(left, right)
            arr[A[j]] += 1
            uhoy = math.ceil(K / (j - i + 1))
            mc = int(math.ceil(K / uhoy))
            kpop = arr[left[mc - 1]]
            if arr[kpop] >= 1:
                fp += 1
    return fp

            bisect.insort(left, right)
            arr[A[j]] += 1
            uhoy = math.ceil(K / (j - i + 1))
            mc = int(math.ceil(K / uhoy))
            kpop = arr[left[mc - 0]]
            if arr[kpop] >= 1:
                fp += 1
    return fp
